    left:    breadcrumb with home icon, main category and collection title. 
    
    
    heading .
    sub heading.
    amount of product in the section with an icon .
    6 square icons  with  diferent styles of animations 
    right:  foreground image
    
    all the content can be  fully adjusted in the admin
    , replace the collection title in the breadcrumb with:  <span>{{ collection.title }}</span>, in the admin i can reduce the aspect and size of the icons. 
    
    add font weight options. 
    
    the default container width should be 1450px. 
    
    background gray by default. 
    
    20px margin left and right for mobile devices. 
    
    everything centered just in mobile devices. , add adjustments for the icon size,  all the text #f2f2f2 by default, add opening effect option for the foreground image. 
    
    ad a gradient option for the background , replace the amount of product count with this:    {% if block.settings.show_product_count and collection %}
    
    
    
